descriptionHtml:
HD reTextures for
- Barset / Counterset
- Bar stool
- Workbench

- Barset / Counterset, Workbench are seamless.
- Added Environmentmap/Cubemap to the Metal parts
- Changed some uv maps of workbench and Barset / Counterset to get little more quality out of it

Stool is 2k
no normal included

bar top is 4k
bar normalmap is 2k
bar envmap is 256x256
update sets it to 512x512

workbenchtop is 4k
workbench normalmap is 1k
workbench envmap is 128x128
